MTA0MDAsImlzU3ViZG9tYWluIjp0cnVlLCJpc1RoaXJkUGFydHkiOnRydWV9\"><meta http-equiv=\"origin-trial\" content=\"A93bovR+QVXNx2/38qDbmeYYf1wdte9EO37K9eMq3r+541qo0byhYU899BhPB7Cv9QqD7wIbR1B6OAc9kEfYCA4AAACQeyJvcmlnaW4iOiJodHRwczovL2dvb2dsZXN5bmRpY2F0aW9uLmNvbTo0NDMiLCJmZWF0dXJlIjoiQUlQcm9tcHRBUElNdWx0aW1vZGFsSW5wdXQiLCJleHBpcnkiOjE3NzQzMTA0MDAsImlzU3ViZG9tYWluIjp0cnVlLCJpc1RoaXJkUGFydHkiOnRydWV9\"><meta http-equiv=\"origin-trial\" content=\"A1S5fojrAunSDrFbD8OfGmFHdRFZymSM/1ss3G+NEttCLfHkXvlcF6LGLH8Mo5PakLO1sCASXU1/gQf6XGuTBgwAAACQeyJvcmlnaW4iOiJodHRwczovL2dvb2dsZXRhZ3NlcnZpY2VzLmNvbTo0NDMiLCJmZWF0dXJlIjoiQUlQcm9tcHRBUElNdWx0aW1vZGFsSW5wdXQiLCJleHBpcnkiOjE3NzQzMTA0MDAsImlzU3ViZG9tYWluIjp0cnVlLCJpc1RoaXJkUGFydHkiOnRydWV9\"></head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"topbar\">Free Malaysia loan calculators for education and planning. Results are estimates only.</div>\n<header class=\"navbar\">\n  <div class=\"nav-inner\">\n    <a class=\"logo\" href=\"index.html\" aria-label=\"LoanCalc Malaysia Home\">\n      <span class=\"logo-mark\">LC</span>\n      <span>LoanCalc Malaysia</span>\n    </a>\n    <nav class=\"nav-links\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\">\n      <a href=\"car-loan-calculator.html\">Car Loan</a>\n      <a href=\"home-loan-calculator.html\">Home Loan</a>\n      <a href=\"legal-fee-stamp-duty-calculator-malaysia.html\">Legal Fees</a>\n      <a href=\"personal-loan-calculator.html\">Personal Loan</a>\n      <a href=\"dsr-calculator.html\">DSR</a>\n      <a href=\"early-settlement-calculator.html\">Settlement</a>\n      <a class=\"nav-cta\" href=\"index.html#calculator\">Calculate Now</a>\n    </nav>\n    <span class=\"mobile-menu-note\">Menu links below</span>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n\n<section class=\"hero\"><div class=\"hero-inner\"><div class=\"car-hero-copy\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Hire Purchase Planning</span><h1>Car Loan Calculator Malaysia</h1><p class=\"hero-text\">Estimate your car loan monthly instalment using vehicle price, down payment, flat interest rate and loan tenure.</p><div class=\"hero-actions\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#calculator\">Calculate Car Loan</a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"index.html\">General Loan Calculator</a></div></div><div class=\"calculator-card\" id=\"calculator\"><h2>Car Loan Calculator</h2><p class=\"small\">Common Malaysian car loan examples often use flat rate estimates.</p><div class=\"form-grid\"><div class=\"field\"><label for=\"carPrice\">Car Price (RM)</label><input id=\"carPrice\" type=\"number\" value=\"80000\" min=\"0\" step=\"1000\"></div><div class=\"field\"><label for=\"carDown\">Down Payment (RM)</label><input id=\"carDown\" type=\"number\" value=\"8000\" min=\"0\" step=\"500\"></div><div class=\"field\"><label for=\"carRate\">Flat Interest Rate (%)</label><input id=\"carRate\" type=\"number\" value=\"3.0\" min=\"0\" step=\"0.01\"></div><div class=\"field\"><label for=\"carYears\">Loan Tenure (Years)</label><input id=\"carYears\" type=\"number\" value=\"7\" min=\"1\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\"></div></div><div class=\"result-grid\"><div class=\"result-box\"><span>Loan Amount</span><strong id=\"carLoanAmount\">RM0.00</strong></div><div class=\"result-box\"><span>Monthly Instalment</span><strong id=\"carMonthly\">RM0.00</strong></div><div class=\"result-box\"><span>Total Interest</span><strong id=\"carInterest\">RM0.00</strong></div></div><div class=\"result-grid\"><div class=\"result-box\"><span>Total Repayment</span><strong id=\"carTotal\">RM0.00</strong></div></div><div class=\"bar-wrap\"><div class=\"bar-principal\"></div><div class=\"bar-interest\"></div></div><div class=\"legend\"><span><i class=\"dot dot-principal\"></i>Loan amount</span><span><i class=\"dot dot-interest\"></i>Estimated interest</span></div><div class=\"alert\">Car loan rules, interest rate, insurance and fees may vary by bank, vehicle type and applicant profile.</div></div></div></section>\n<section class=\"section\"><div class=\"content-card\"><h2>How to Estimate Car Loan Monthly Instalment</h2><p>A car loan calculator helps you estimate monthly instalment before buying a new or used vehicle. The main inputs are vehicle price, down payment, flat interest rate and tenure.</p><div class=\"formula\">Estimated loan amount = car price - down payment<br>Total interest = loan amount × flat rate × years<br>Monthly instalment = (loan amount + total interest) ÷ months</div><p>For example, a lower down payment increases the financed amount and may increase monthly instalment. A longer tenure can reduce monthly instalment but usually increases total interest.</p></div>\n<div class=\"content-card\"><h2>Car Loan Planning Tips</h2><ul><li>Compare monthly instalment against your monthly income and existing commitments.</li><li>Check whether the quoted interest rate is a flat rate or effective rate.</li><li>Prepare extra budget for insurance, road tax, service, maintenance and fuel.</li><li>Avoid choosing a car based only on monthly instalment.</li></ul></div></section>\n<section class=\"section\"><div class=\"section-head\"><h2>Car Loan FAQ</h2></div><div class=\"faq-list\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Is this car loan calculator using flat rate?</summary><p>Yes. This page estimates car loan instalment using a simple flat rate method, which is commonly used for car financing examples.</p></details><details><summary>Does the result include insurance?</summary><p>No. The estimate does not include insurance, road tax, processing fees or other charges.</p></details><details><summary>Can I use this for used cars?</summary><p>Yes, you can use it for simple used car estimates, but actual rates and margin of finance may be different.</p></details><details><summary>Is a 9-year car loan better?</summary><p>A longer tenure can lower monthly instalment, but it may increase total interest and keep you in debt for a longer period.</p></details></div></section>\n\n\n\n\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"footer-inner\">\n    <div>\n      <h3>LoanCalc Malaysia</h3>\n      <p>Free Malaysia loan calculators and practical guides to estimate repayment, interest cost, DSR and affordability before making a financing decision.</p>\n      <p class=\"small\">This website is for general educational use only and does not provide financial advice.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <h4>Calculators</h4>\n      <a href=\"index.html\">Loan Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"car-loan-calculator.html\">Car Loan Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"home-loan-calculator.html\">Home Loan Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"legal-fee-stamp-duty-calculator-malaysia.html\">Legal Fee &amp; Stamp Duty Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"personal-loan-calculator.html\">Personal Loan Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"dsr-calculator.html\">DSR Calculator</a>\n      <a href=\"early-settlement-calculator.html\">Early Settlement Calculator</a><a href=\"valuation-fee-calculator-malaysia.html\">Valuation Fee Calculator</a>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <h4>Guides &amp; Site</h4>\n      <a href=\"guides.html\">Loan Guides</a>\n      <a href=\"loan-affordability-malaysia.html\">Loan Affordability Guide</a>\n      <a href=\"about.html\">About</a>\n      <a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n      <a href=\"privacy.html\">Privacy Policy</a>\n      <a href=\"disclaimer.html\">Disclaimer</a>\n      <a href=\"terms-of-use.html\">Terms of Use</a>\n      <a href=\"sitemap.xml\">Sitemap</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"copyright\">© 2026 LoanCalc Malaysia. All rights reserved.</div>\n</footer>\n<script src=\"assets/js/main.js\"></script><ins class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-hi=\"true\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: none !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_0_host\" style=\"border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; height: 0px; width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block;\"></div></ins>\n\n\n\n\n</body></html>",
